Description_lang: Raszageth marks players with a $@spellname399713 for $d. Upon expiration, it inflicts $399711s1 Nature damage to all players and pulls them to the location of the blast. This damage is reduced the further away players are from the blast.
AuraDescription_lang: Upon expiration, inflicts up to $399711s1 Nature damage and pulls players to your location. This damage is reduced the further away players are from the blast.
